#******************************************************************
#
#

SCHEDULE AFICI-AF#SAPCAIEASTRE54 
ON REQUEST
UNTIL 2359 
CARRYFORWARD
:
#
#Creation du fichier recu dans le repertoire in de SAP

AFICI-AF#SAPCAILANCEINSAPEASTRE54
OPENS AFICI-AF#"/transfert/reception/ASTREPRI_SAPPRI200_EASTRE54"

PRI#SAPCAIZCAI_EASTRE54
 FOLLOWS SAPCAILANCEINSAPEASTRE54

#Envoi du fichier vers la gateway
#^S01FLU^VGB17"
#outSAP"
#FOLLOWS SAPCAIOUTSAPSASTRE51

AFICI-AF#SAPCAIGATEWAYSASTRE51
 FOLLOWS SAPCAIZCAI_EASTRE54
END

ON REQUEST
:
PCI#SRX_PSALAF_D_RENOMEBSPMAD
OPENS PCI#"/transfert/reception/AF057/ACKPEV122-EBSPMAD*" (`ls %p | wc -w` -gt 0)

PCI#SRX_PSALAF_D_MOVEEBSPMAD
OPENS PCI#"/transfert/reception/AF057/BSPPCI_SAPPCI100_EBSPMAD*" (`ls %p | wc -w` -gt 0)
 FOLLOWS SRX_PSALAF_D_RENOMEBSPMAD

PCI#SRX_PSALAF_D_RNOMEEBSPMAD
 FOLLOWS SRX_PSALAF_D_MOVEEBSPMAD

PCI#SRX_PSALAF_D_RMEBSPMAD
 FOLLOWS SRX_PSALAF_D_RNOMEEBSPMAD
END

 FOLLOWS SAPCOCOPYECARAIB02

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOARCHECARAIB02
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ03ECARAIB02

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOSSAPCO02SUPP
 FOLLOWS SAPCOARCHECARAIB02
END

#Excution du programme ZCOERJ01

SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOECARAIB03 
ON RUNCYCLE RULE1 "FREQ=DAILY;"
UNTIL 0005 
:
#Fichier venant de caraib

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOCOPYECARAIB03
OPENS QVIPCOR1#"/transfert/PRD200/SAPCO/tmp/SSAPCO03_SAPCOPRD" (`ls %p | wc -w` -gt 0 )

#Integration des donnes vol - fichier ECARAIB03

PRD#SAPCOZCOERG01ECARAIB03
OPENS QVIPCOR1#"/transfert/PRD200/CARAIB/in/ECARAIB03_CARAIBPRD" (`ls %p | wc -w` -gt 0 )
 FOLLOWS SAPCOCOPYECARAIB03

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOARCHECARAIB03
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERG01ECARAIB03

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOSUPFICECARAIB03
 FOLLOWS SAPCOARCHECARAIB03

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOSSAPCO03SUPP
 FOLLOWS SAPCOSUPFICECARAIB03
END

#Excution du programme ZCOECF20

SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOECARAIB04 
ON RUNCYCLE RULE1 "FREQ=DAILY;"
UNTIL 0005 
:
#Reception flux RGVC21

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOLANCEINSAPECARAIB04
OPENS QVIPCOR1#"/transfert/reception/CARAIBPRD_SAPPRD200_ECARAI04" (`ls %p | wc -w` -gt 0 )

#Dcoupage du fichier ECARAI06 pour COPA

PRD#SAPCOZCOECF20ECARAIB04
 FOLLOWS SAPCOLANCEINSAPECARAIB04
END

#Execution du programme ZCOCON01, puis decoupage et transco des fichiers ECARAI
#05 et ECARAI06.

SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOECARAIB05 
ON RUNCYCLE RULE1 "FREQ=DAILY;"
UNTIL 1800 +1 DAYS 
CARRYFORWARD
:
#Reception flux RGVC22

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOLANCEINSAPECARAIB05
OPENS QVIPCOR1#"/transfert/reception/CARAIBPRD_SAPPRD200_ECARAI05" (`ls %p | wc -w` -gt 0 )

#Reception flux RGVC21

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOLANCEINSAPECARAIB06
OPENS QVIPCOR1#"/transfert/reception/CARAIBPRD_SAPPRD200_ECARAI06"

#Elaboration de l etat de contrtle double Flux

PRD#SAPCOZCOCON01ECARAIB05
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCODPR01ECARAIB05

#Decoupage du fichier ECARAI05 pour COPA

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ10ECARAIB05
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOCON01ECARAIB05

#Mise au format COPA du fichier ECARAI0B5 decoupe

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ01ECARAIB05_1
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ECARAIB05

#Mise au format COPA du fichier ECARAIB05 decoupe

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ01ECARAIB05_2
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ECARAIB05

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ01ECARAIB05_3
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ECARAIB05

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ01ECARAIB05_4
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ECARAIB05

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ01ECARAIB05_5
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ECARAIB05

#Suppression du fichier ECARAIB05

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOECARAIB05SUPP
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ECARAIB05

#Decoupage du fichier ECARAI06 pour COPA

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ10ECARAIB06
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOCON01ECARAIB05

#Mise au format COPA du fichier ECARAI06 decoupe

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ01ECARAIB06_1
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ECARAIB06

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ01ECARAIB06_2
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ECARAIB06

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ01ECARAIB06_3
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ECARAIB06

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ01ECARAIB06_4
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ECARAIB06

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ01ECARAIB06_5
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ECARAIB06

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOECARAIB06SUPP
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ECARAIB06

#Mise  jour des variables priode et exercice dans TVARC

PRD#SAPCOZCODPR01ECARAIB05
 FOLLOWS SAPCOLANCEINSAPECARAIB05
 FOLLOWS SAPCOLANCEINSAPECARAIB06
END

UNTIL 0005

 FOLLOWS SAPCOLANCEINSAPECARAIB09

#  Date:          September 26th, 2000
#
#*******************************************************************************
#
# SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOESAFFI09 - Couts Distrib. Fret SAFFIR -> Deversement CCA
# I-04-20
#
#
# SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOESAFFI09
#

SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOESAFFI09 
ON RUNCYCLE RULE1 "FREQ=DAILY"
UNTIL 2359 
:
#
# Creation du fichier recu dans le repertoire in de SAP

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOLANCEINSAPESAFFI09
 EVERY 0015
OPENS QVIPCOR1#"^S00REC^/SAFFI^S00HTMT^_ESAFFI09"

#
# Programme ZCOECF10

PRD#SAPCOZCOECF10ESAFFI09
 EVERY 0015
 FOLLOWS SAPCOLANCEINSAPESAFFI09
END

#*******************************************************************************
#
#SCHEDULE SAPCOESAFFI09
#
#        ON EVERYDAY
#        UNTIL 2359
#        PRIORITY 10
#:
#
# Creation du fichier recu dans le repertoire in de SAP
#        SAPCOLANCEINSAPESAFFI09
#                OPENS QVIPCOR1#"^S00REC^/SAFFI^S00HTMT^_ESAFFI09"
#                EVERY 15
#
# Creation des dossiers batch-input
#        PRD#SAPCOZCOECF10ESAFFI09
#                FOLLOWS SAPCOLANCEINSAPESAFFI09
#                EVERY 15
#
# Execution du dossier de batch input
#        SAPCORSBDCSUB1ESAFFI09
#                FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOECF10ESAFFI09
#                EVERY 15
#END
#
#*********************************************************************************
#******************************************************************************
#  Air France SAP
#
#  Developed by AIR FRANCE Toulouse
#
#  Module Name:   MAESTRO Master Schedule for SAP Daily processing
#
#  Date:          September 26th, 2000
#
#**********************************************************************************
# SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOESAFFI11 - Saffir Retrofit
#

SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOESAFFI11 
ON RUNCYCLE RULE1 "FREQ=DAILY"
UNTIL 2359 
:
#
# Creation du fichier recu dans le repertoire in de SAP

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOLANCEINSAPESAFFI11
 EVERY 0015
OPENS QVIPCOR1#"^S00REC^/SAFFI^S00HTMT^_ESAFFI11"

#
# Creation des dossiers batch-input

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ01ESAFFI11
 EVERY 0015
 FOLLOWS SAPCOLANCEINSAPESAFFI11
END

SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOESIRAX01_B 
DESCRIPTION "Integration des fichiers SIRAX pour SAPCO"
ON RUNCYCLE RULE1 "FREQ=DAILY;INTERVAL=1"
UNTIL 2359 
:
QVIPCOR1#SAPCOLANCEINSAPESIRAX01
OPENS QVIPCOR1#"/transfert/reception/SIRAXPRD_SAPPRD200_ESIRAX01" (-f %p)

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOLANCEINSAPESIRAX02
OPENS QVIPCOR1#"/transfert/reception/SIRAXPRD_SAPPRD200_ESIRAX02" (-f %p)

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOLANCEINSAPESIRAX03
OPENS QVIPCOR1#"/transfert/reception/SIRAXPRD_SAPPRD200_ESIRAX03" (-f %p)

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOLANCEINSAPESIRAX06
OPENS QVIPCOR1#"/transfert/reception/SIRAXPRD_SAPPRD200_ESIRAX06" (-f %p)

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOLANCEINSAPESIRAX07
OPENS QVIPCOR1#"/transfert/reception/SIRAXPRD_SAPPRD200_ESIRAX07" (-f %p)

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ10ESIRAX01
 FOLLOWS SAPCOLANCEINSAPESIRAX01

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ10ESIRAX02
 FOLLOWS SAPCOLANCEINSAPESIRAX02

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ10ESIRAX06
 FOLLOWS SAPCOLANCEINSAPESIRAX06

PRD#SAPCOZCOERJ10ESIRAX07
 FOLLOWS SAPCOLANCEINSAPESIRAX07

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOESIRAX01SUPP
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ESIRAX01

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOESIRAX02SUPP
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ESIRAX02

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOESIRAX06SUPP
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ESIRAX06

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOESIRAX07SUPP
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ESIRAX07

 FOLLOWS SAPCOESIRAX01SUPP

 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOERJ10ESIRAX02

#Excution du programme ZCOESX01

SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOESIRAX05 
ON RUNCYCLE RULE1 "FREQ=DAILY;"
UNTIL 0005 
OPENS QVIPCOR1#"/transfert/reception/SIRAXPRD_SAPPRD200_ESIRAX05" (`ls %p | wc -w` -gt 0 )
:
QVIPCOR1#SAPCOLANCEINSAPESIRAX05

PRD#SAPCOZCOSRX01ESIRAX05
 FOLLOWS SAPCOLANCEINSAPESIRAX05

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOESIRAX05SUPP
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOSRX01ESIRAX05
END

UNTIL 2359 
:

PRD#SAPCOZCOERM20ESOCLE02
 EVERY 0015
 FOLLOWS SAPCOLANCEINSAPESOCLE02
END

#Transcodification du fichier STAR23_ZCOERJ10_1

 FOLLOWS SAPCOZHCOBORH01
END

#***************************************************************************
#*********************************************************************
#Air France SAP
#
#Developed by AIR FRANCE Toulouse
#
#Module Name:   MAESTRO Master Schedule for SAP Daily processing
#
#Date:          September 26th, 2000
#
#**************************************************************************
#
#SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOSGIP01 - Transfert Centres de couts SAP vers GIP et RDJ
#I-02-01 (Interface sortante)
#
#

SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOSGIP01 
ON RUNCYCLE RULE1 "FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=TU,WE,TH,FR,SA"
AT 0200 UNTIL 0500 
:
#Lancement du programme ZCOSGI10

PRD#SAPCOZCOSGI10SGIP01

#OPENS QVIPCOR1#"/transfert/^S00HOST^^S00MANDT^/GIP/out/SGIP01_GIP^S00ORIG^"
#
#Copie du fichier pour envoi a VULCAIN

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOCOPIESGIP01
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOSGI10SGIP01

#
#Envoi du fichier vers pelunix pour Vulcain

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOGWVLBSGIP11
 FOLLOWS SAPCOGWVLBSGIP01

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOGWVLBSGIP01
 FOLLOWS SAPCOCOPIESGIP01
END

#*********************************************************************
#**************************************************************************
#Air France SAP
#
#Developed by AIR FRANCE Toulouse
#
#Module Name:   MAESTRO Master Schedule for SAP Daily processing
#
#Date:          September 26th, 2000
#
#**************************************************************************
#
#SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOSGIP02 - Transfert Centres de couts SAP vers GIP et RDJ
#I-02-01 (Interface sortante)
#le programme ABAP est lance manuellement par un utilisateur.
#
#

SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOSGIP02 
ON RUNCYCLE RULE1 "FREQ=DAILY;"
UNTIL 0005 
:
#
#Suppression fichier Avis

QVIPCOR1#SAPCORMSGIP02
 EVERY 0005
 FOLLOWS SAPCOGWVLBSGIP02

#
#Envoi du fichier vers pelunix

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOGWVLBSGIP02
 EVERY 0005
OPENS QVIPCOR1#"/transfert/PRD200/GIP/out/SGIP02_GIPPRD" (`ls %p | wc -w` -gt 0 )
END

 FOLLOWS SAPCOGWVLBSPROVI05
END

#************************************************************************
#
#SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOSSAPCO01 - controle integrite sur ordre interne entre S
#AP et RDJ
#I-02-02
#
#Air France SAP
#
#Developed by AIR FRANCE Toulouse
#
#Module Name:   MAESTRO Master Schedule for SAP Daily processing
#
#Date:	September 26th, 2000
#
#Modif:	01 octobre 2004		Changement du nom de la copie du fichier pour Vulcain
#
#************************************************************************
#
#

SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOSSAPCO01 
ON REQUEST
AT 0030 UNTIL 2359 
:
#
#Lancement du programme ZCOSOR01

PRD#SAPCOZCOSOR01SSAPCO01

#
#Copie du fichier pour envoi a VULCAIN

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOCOPIESSAPCO01
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOSOR01SSAPCO01

#
#Envoi du fichier vers Vilgenis

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOGWVLBSSAPCO01
 FOLLOWS SAPCOCOPIESSAPCO01

#
#Envoi du fichier vers Vulcain
#

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOGWVLBSSAPCO11
 FOLLOWS SAPCOGWVLBSSAPCO01
END

#Gnration et envoi des fichiers SSAPCO10 et SSAPCO11 par le programme ZCOSO
#R01

SCHEDULE QVIPCOR1#SAPCOSSAPCO10 
ON RUNCYCLE RULE1 "FREQ=DAILY;"
AT 0400 UNTIL 2359 
:
#Lancement du programme ZCOSOR01 qui gnre le fichier SSAPCO10

PRD#SAPCOZCOSOR01SSAPCO10

#Cration par copie du fichier  SSAPCO11

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOCOPIESSAPCO10
 FOLLOWS SAPCOZCOSOR01SSAPCO10

#Envoi du fichier SSAPCO11 vers le flux XFB RVGG03 pour RDJ

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOGWVLBSSAPCO10
 FOLLOWS SAPCOCOPIESSAPCO10

#Envoi du fichier SSAPCO11 vers le flux XFB RUVSV2 pour Vulcain

QVIPCOR1#SAPCOGWVLBSSAPCO11
 FOLLOWS SAPCOGWVLBSSAPCO10
END

END

 FOLLOWS SAPMMZMADRA01RACAJ02

 FOLLOWS SAPMMZMADRA01RACAJ03

QVIPCOR1#SAPMMFINDEMOISRACA01
 FOLLOWS SAPMMZMADRA01RACAJ02

#
#* Reception automatique des commandes achats (mensuel) type commandes NB

#* Schedule    : TRF_DCTSNR
#
#* Application : Trafic
#
#* Statut      : RECETTE
#
#* Description : Identification des contrats NR (non renouveles)
#                35 minutes apres le JNEXTDAY
#
#* Consigne    : Appliquer la consigne doc d'exploit chap Schedules et jobs
#                Maestro
#************************************************************
#         EXCEPT  TRFEXCPT

ON RUNCYCLE RULE1 "FREQ=DAILY;"
UNTIL 0005 
:
TRAFIC#TRF_D_CTS_IDEN_NR
OPENS TRAFIC#"/app/TRAFIC/data/tws_ok/OK_CONTRATS_NR_START"
 FOLLOWS TRAFIC#TRF_DDATMAJ.TRF_D_DAT_MAJ_PROC 
END

#        EXCEPT  TRFEXCPT

 FOLLOWS TRAFIC#TRF_DCTSRT.TRF_D_CTS_IDEN_RT
